ch.ethz.inspire.emod.model

Class Material

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.ethz.inspire.emod.model.Material

  • public class Material
extends java.lang.Object
    General Material model class. Provides fluid properties Assumptions: -Newtonian fluid -Pressure influence on viscosity neglected -Density influenced by pressure and temperature Config parameters: TemperaturSamples: [Kelvin] PressureSamples: [Pa] Initialviscosity: [mm2/s] Initialdensity: [kg/m3]
    Author:
    sizuest, based on HydraulicOil
